      "content": "Boston Stadium 门票现已发售 |Ticombo Boston Stadium 张门票 14 六月 2026 - 10 七月 2026 Boston Stadium 张门票 14 六月 2026 - 10 七月 2026 最热门 6月-7月 13-9 周六-周四 Boston Stadium 7 Matches World Cup 2026 Boston Stadium Boston, US 2 门票起¥15,446 购买 6月 19 周五 Scotland vs Morocco - World Cup 2026 - M30 Group C Boston Stadium Boston, US 1385 门票起¥5,972 购买 6月 23 周二 England vs Ghana - World Cup 2026 - M45 Group L Boston Stadium Boston, US 1360 门票起¥6,330 购买 6月 26 周五 Norway vs France - World Cup 2026 - M61 Group I Boston Stadium Boston, US 971 门票起¥8,062 购买 6月 29 周一 Round of 32 1E vs 3ABCDF - World Cup 2026 - M74 Boston Stadium Boston, US 1350 门票起¥5,912 购买 7月 9 周四 Quarterfinal W89 vs W90 World Cup 2026 - M97 Boston Stadium Boston, US 882 门票起¥13,138 购买",
